:

1. Ona mu je prećutala da je laž *laž* (She kept quiet about his lie.).
2. On je večito laži i obmanjuje druge *laž* (He is always lying and deceiving others.).
3. Bezobrazno je lažno obećanje *laž* (It's rude to make a false promise.).
4. Oni su otkrili lažne izjave *laž* (They uncovered false statements.).
5. Ne mogu da poverujem da bi on izmislio takvu laž *laž* (I can't believe he would make up such a lie.).